column5: We got out tonight for a fun fish with some friends!  The weather has certainly been co operating and so have the fish.  The boys had a blast...  We got a lot of hits, missed some but landed 15 fish of all different sizes.   They did a great job catching and netting their own fish!    Even a double header or two:)      Thanks to Steve for taking us out, it was a great night had by all!  Cheers  Bernadette
All these reports of huge numbers of catfish makes me bummed that I only caught two... Nice going.
